It can be observed that the development of common prosperity in the Zhejiang province—Hangzhou, Ningbo, Jiaxing, Shaoxing, Wenzhou, Huzhou, Taizhou, Quzhou, Jinhua, Zhoushan, and Lishui—ranges from high to relatively low.
